{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b1731bb6-b7a7-406f-a4c2-56f14e5d0fef","content":"Yes, you'll hit compatibility issues. Here's the breakdown:\n\n**Framework Support in MSTest v3:**\n- ✅ `net462` — supported\n- ❌ `net5.0` — **not supported** (MSTest v3 requires .NET 6.0+)\n- ❌ `netcoreapp3.1` — **not supported** (end-of-life runtime)\n\nMSTest v3 dropped support for out-of-support .NET runtimes. You'd need to update your target frameworks to at least `net6.0` (or ideally `net8.0`/`net9.0`) to replace `net5.0` and `netcoreapp3.1`.\n\n**Other migration notes:**\n- MSTest v3 offers a single `MSTest` meta-package replacing the separate `MSTest.TestFramework` + `MSTest.TestAdapter` references.\n- There are some breaking API/behavioral changes (e.g., stricter test lifecycle, class/assembly cleanup defaults).\n\n**Minimum viable change** to your `TargetFrameworks`:\n```\nnet8.0;net462\n```\n\nWould you like me to update the project file for the migration?","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"051004d0-4dd6-43ac-af17-69de7ea09a29","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The project targets `net5.0`, `net462`, and `netcoreapp3.1`. The user wants to migrate to MSTest v3. Let me think about compatibility issues:\n\n1. **MSTest v3 dropped support for older frameworks.** MSTest v3 requires at minimum:\n   - .NET 6.0+ (for .NET Core/modern .NET)\n   - .NET Framework 4.6.2+ (this should be fine since they have net462)\n   - `netcoreapp3.1` and `net5.0` are NOT supported by MSTest v3.\n\n2. MSTest v3 consolidated packages - instead of separate `MSTest.TestFramework` and `MSTest.TestAdapter`, you use a single `MSTest` meta-package (though the individual packages still exist).\n\n\n3. There are also breaking API changes in MSTest v3 with some attributes renamed and behavior modifications. The core issue here is framework compatibility—MSTest v3 dropped support for `netcoreapp3.1` and `net5.0` since both are end-of-life. Only `net462` would be compatible, while the other two target frameworks would fail to work with MSTest v3.","outputTokens":659,"requestId":"7C20:203FDB:2C5758C:314FF07:69F95AD2"},"id":"6bff6ed1-e836-41fc-821e-c83e7bfcb2c1","timestamp":"2026-05-05T02:50:09.612Z","parentId":"a964968a-57b1-4dd1-a1cf-cc4490a9ee01"}
